nodes.text: Nel Frel was a Sullustan who was a member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic who served as the captain of the Stellar Crawler, a modified YT-2400 light freighter. Frel was part of Rebel Alliance Intelligence Service, and was involved in Operation Night Fire, a mission to steal a state-of-the-art Imperial spy ship, the Darkflare, under construction at a Sienar Fleet Systems orbital shipyard.
